[+++ b/spring-boot-docs/src/main/asciidoc/appendix-configuration-metadata.adoc, +, +|`spring-profile-name`, +|Auto-complete the available profile names in the project., +, +NOTE: The binder is not aware of the meta-data so if you provide that hint, you, +will still need to transform the bean name into an actual Bean reference using, +the `ApplicationContext`., +, +===== Spring profile name, +The **spring-profile-name** provider auto-completes the Spring profiles that are, +defined in the configuration of the current project., +, +The meta-data snippet below corresponds to the standard `spring.profiles.active`, +property that defines the name of the Spring profile(s) to enable:, +, +[source,json,indent=0], +----, +	{"hints": [, +		{, +			"name": "spring.profiles.active",, +			"providers": [, +				{, +					"name": "spring-profile-name", +				}, +			], +		}, +	]}, +----, +]